{"tid":463730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果片同文唔match　編輯老屈梁天琦","createTime":"2017-11-09T19:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T16:35:01.000Z","uid":47714,"like":91,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9bcf04035ee7ab9f74a3c558a133c9645f0a1684","tid":463730,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:32:57.000Z","msg":"蘋果條片同新聞稿唔match<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/11/09/3479740/20171109_news_04_240p.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F3479740%2F20171109_news_04_240p.mp4&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNv9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=295ac410\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/11/09/3479740/20171109_news_04_240p.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n睇到聽到片中梁天琦係咁講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/nyHKUW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnyHKUW&h=aec7a337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雨傘完結之後　當o係一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/snV9FJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsnV9FJ&h=710e176a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或是基本法o既框架底下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/YFT51z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FYFT51z&h=17c67398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n追求香港民主o既夢碎o左啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/UcAXvb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FUcAXvb&h=be96b87a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\no係一個咁樣o既環境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/fNwSVb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfNwSVb&h=abec7c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先至有越o黎越多香港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/NcVbPY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FNcVbPY&h=fe304759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n追求支持香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/PuJou6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FPuJou6&h=56624453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似我咁樣曾經有講過呢四隻字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/dYYfrH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdYYfrH&h=c39f7eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁就要冇o左　咁就要失去自己一個政治權利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/k4h6zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fk4h6zh&h=c51046e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係有好多人睇唔過眼呢種咁o既控制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/Dp1gLh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FDp1gLh&h=6a71fd90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做事手法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/QXrFFN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FQXrFFN&h=d04fd279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以先至會轉移去追求香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦係講點解突然多o左人追求香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n而蘋果新聞文字稿就變成「認為如果香港一早落實真普選，港人就不會有要求獨立的想法」<br />\n<br />\nＡ－＞Ｂ =/= not Ａ－＞ not Ｂ<br />\n<br />\n只係基本邏輯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦講o左兩個因素<br />\n但亦有人講為o左反殖　保存香港文化同價值觀念　諸如此類<br />\n<br />\n好似我咁　一早個高登名就係「五獨通過」　只係雨革果陣面前有可望立即達到o既目標之後更有助獨立　人地問香港人有冇支持港獨　我先冇出聲"},{"pid":"9b3fba7ffbe2208638f033acc4c198c193a67eb9","tid":463730,"uid":33610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:05:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0263fb86e8e2d7516e7b0c5214c0de43a576ec26","tid":463730,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40516274d339c4c523df1869e7952d254b8751b5","tid":463730,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"毒果報有名叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e60e051a568f702c7db7105bdefa9769c99996e","tid":463730,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:56:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛打曬飛機</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7cee84a0267426670c70b95037a58862e6e7fb02