覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e20e0437d5331b014f409207099b3da9b68155c","tid":463730,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T19:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一日識販民？"},{"pid":"5711eec64c22726387e2ee9ddb8998bb2e87f56a","tid":463730,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>在講座中，他多次提到自己目前已不再推動香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n成個講座咁耐，你確定條片就係全部內容？<br />\n我都唔肯定因為我唔在場<br />\n但我傾向相信佢講座至少提過一次<br />\n尤其係報導出左街唔見佢澄清</blockquote><br />\n既然梁天琦講過咁多次點解唔直接播返句嘢出嚟呢？<br />\n要咁樣轉述？</blockquote><br />\n可以好多原因<br />\n你留意下呢段片係佢直接同緊蘋果記者講野既片<br />\n冇包到會上各人發言<br />\n報導就話佢係會上講冇再推動港獨<br />\n冇包到唔出奇</blockquote><br />\n既然係咁點解唔直接播果段出黎，要咁大個圈黎講？<br />\n同埋毒果抹黑本土 港獨唔係今日先知既事，上次星火單野都唔澄清啦（講都費是）<br />\n如果有講仲唔放大黎講？<br />\n你好似信哂毒果咁"},{"pid":"aeed65f0d4726b64b5a2bfa455c3d20e9e52b42b","tid":463730,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580b5e4785eaa5b8c4310d53c14ca6cc72bae141","tid":463730,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}